com.halseyburgund.rwframework.core
Class RWTags

java.lang.Object
  com.halseyburgund.rwframework.core.RWTags

public class RWTags
extends java.lang.Object

Project tags data. Consists of a number of tags for the active modes (listen, speak) and all types (questions, gender, age, etc.). Each tag has a number of options, of which none, one or multiple can be selected. The tag_id of selected options is supposed to be unique and included in server calls.

Author:
Rob Knapen
